[Student "S"]
{EAST has a strong hand, 20 points and balanced distribution. 
It is just right to open 2NT (20-21 points).

WEST adds her 2 points to EAST's promised number of 20 or 21. Since she doesn't reach the 
magic game number of 26 points she just passes.}

